1
00:00:00,930 --> 00:00:02,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so relieved.</font>

2
00:00:02,970 --> 00:00:08,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your spirit isn't broken. You've only 
cautiously locked yourself away.</font>

3
00:00:08,630 --> 00:00:10,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Am I wrong,</font>

4
00:00:10,460 --> 00:00:12,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pamela Francis?</font>

5
00:00:13,920 --> 00:00:16,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you want revenge?</font>

6
00:00:18,750 --> 00:00:23,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Revenge on the one who did this 
to you: Constance Grail?</font>

7
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:30,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Constance Grail!</font>

8
00:02:04,480 --> 00:02:06,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Lordship, how is Kimberly?</font>

9
00:02:07,220 --> 00:02:08,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Safe.</font>

10
00:02:08,350 --> 00:02:12,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Her arm was injured, but she should 
be out of the hospital soon.</font>

11
00:02:12,140 --> 00:02:13,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank goodness!</font>

12
00:02:14,700 --> 00:02:21,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That ledger allowed us to arrest Simon 
Darkian for falsifying official documents.</font>

13
00:02:21,790 --> 00:02:25,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His wife, Deborah, has been sent 
to the Rudolph Convent</font>

14
00:02:25,750 --> 00:02:30,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">on suspicion of human trafficking 
and smuggling Jackal's Paradise.</font>

15
00:02:30,630 --> 00:02:35,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This ought to strip Daeg Gallus 
of its biggest backer.</font>

16
00:02:40,190 --> 00:02:42,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How are you fine ladies today?</font>

17
00:02:42,640 --> 00:02:44,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lucia!</font>

18
00:02:44,270 --> 00:02:45,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're going out?</font>

19
00:02:45,650 --> 00:02:51,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes! I'm going to buy sweets for Abby,
since she's been so busy!</font>

20
00:02:51,750 --> 00:02:54,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, if you'll excuse me.</font>

21
00:02:55,660 --> 00:02:59,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't believe the Darkians 
were a party to smuggling.</font>

22
00:03:00,180 --> 00:03:02,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Debby didn't used to be like that.</font>

23
00:03:05,320 --> 00:03:09,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, did Simon know where 
to find Prince Ulysses?</font>

24
00:03:09,910 --> 00:03:15,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, and we have mere days 
before the Farisian delegation departs.</font>

25
00:03:16,110 --> 00:03:18,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we don't locate 
the prince before then...</font>

26
00:03:19,040 --> 00:03:21,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It will mean war?</font>

27
00:03:24,560 --> 00:03:28,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do any Daeg Gallus collaborators 
control a harbor?</font>

28
00:03:28,900 --> 00:03:29,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why a harbor?</font>

29
00:03:31,460 --> 00:03:36,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The kidnapper is a merchant with 
an unusual skin tone by our standards,</font>

30
00:03:36,860 --> 00:03:39,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">yet not a soul has reported seeing him.</font>

31
00:03:40,370 --> 00:03:46,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, suppose the prince is someplace 
a man like that wouldn't stand out.</font>

32
00:03:47,330 --> 00:03:49,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's her idea. Does it help?</font>

33
00:03:49,580 --> 00:03:52,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course! Kiara Grafton.</font>

34
00:03:52,970 --> 00:03:55,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's a wharf on her family's lands.</font>

35
00:03:55,560 --> 00:03:57,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! With the Daeg Gallus tattoo!</font>

36
00:03:58,470 --> 00:04:01,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She must have warehouses 
perfect for hiding a person.</font>

37
00:04:02,610 --> 00:04:03,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll go investigate.</font>

38
00:04:04,470 --> 00:04:06,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I... I'll go with you!</font>

39
00:04:10,540 --> 00:04:11,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Abby!</font>

40
00:04:12,820 --> 00:04:15,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank goodness. You're all right?</font>

41
00:04:15,100 --> 00:04:16,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why wouldn't I be?</font>

42
00:04:16,780 --> 00:04:18,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I got a tip.</font>

43
00:04:18,440 --> 00:04:22,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Deborah Darkian has escaped
 from the convent.</font>

44
00:04:26,560 --> 00:04:30,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-Are you angry that 
I insisted on coming?</font>

45
00:04:31,520 --> 00:04:34,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No. I was reminding myself</font>

46
00:04:34,700 --> 00:04:39,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that it's better to keep you in my sights
than to let you run off on your own.</font>

47
00:04:39,970 --> 00:04:41,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He has a point.</font>

48
00:04:44,380 --> 00:04:45,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That said,</font>

49
00:04:46,040 --> 00:04:49,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I may not need to keep an eye
 on you much longer.</font>

50
00:04:51,590 --> 00:04:56,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When we locate Prince Ulysses 
and all of this is resolved,</font>

51
00:04:56,020 --> 00:04:58,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the two of you will have
 achieved your goal too.</font>

52
00:04:59,680 --> 00:05:00,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So...</font>

53
00:05:01,990 --> 00:05:03,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't want to hear this.</i></font>

54
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:09,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I'll arrange things for you to dissolve
our engagement when the time comes.</font>

55
00:05:10,070 --> 00:05:12,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Such that no blame falls 
on you, of course.</font>

56
00:05:15,370 --> 00:05:17,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about Your Lordship?</font>

57
00:05:21,520 --> 00:05:24,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Won't you marry?</font>

58
00:05:28,190 --> 00:05:32,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No. I have no faith that 
I could make a wife happy.</font>

59
00:05:38,570 --> 00:05:40,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a silly man.</font>

60
00:05:43,520 --> 00:05:46,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You certainly bought a lot, Lady Lucia.</font>

61
00:05:46,190 --> 00:05:50,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Indeed! I just know Abby will love these!</font>

62
00:05:51,530 --> 00:05:52,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come now!</font>

63
00:05:53,280 --> 00:05:55,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll retrieve it at once!</font>

64
00:06:06,540 --> 00:06:08,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know you.</font>

65
00:06:08,670 --> 00:06:11,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Raise your voice and I'll slit her throat.</font>

66
00:06:11,580 --> 00:06:13,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">L-Lady Lucia...</font>

67
00:06:15,800 --> 00:06:19,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kindly release that woman, Lady Deborah.</font>

68
00:06:19,040 --> 00:06:21,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's me you're after, is it not?</font>

69
00:06:27,390 --> 00:06:29,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, this is the warehouse.</font>

70
00:06:29,600 --> 00:06:31,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's awfully quiet.</font>

71
00:06:32,380 --> 00:06:34,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll take a peek inside.</font>

72
00:06:36,360 --> 00:06:37,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Connie.</font>

73
00:06:37,720 --> 00:06:39,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right.</font>

74
00:06:49,260 --> 00:06:50,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Run!</font>

75
00:06:58,260 --> 00:06:59,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you all right?</font>

76
00:06:59,260 --> 00:07:00,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yes.</font>

77
00:07:00,740 --> 00:07:01,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Connie!</font>

78
00:07:06,490 --> 00:07:07,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where are they firing from?!</font>

79
00:07:07,910 --> 00:07:09,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Over there!</font>

80
00:07:09,230 --> 00:07:11,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She says there's one on that roof!</font>

81
00:07:17,020 --> 00:07:18,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Laid an ambush for us, did they?</font>

82
00:07:18,990 --> 00:07:22,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I saw signs that they moved in a hurry. 
They caught wind of us.</font>

83
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:27,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll draw their attention. 
You escape in the meantime.</font>

84
00:07:29,280 --> 00:07:32,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Scarlett, look after Miss Grail.</font>

85
00:07:32,380 --> 00:07:33,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

86
00:07:48,860 --> 00:07:49,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Lordship!</font>

87
00:07:49,980 --> 00:07:51,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't lose your head!</font>

88
00:07:52,020 --> 00:07:54,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you think you can do?!</font>

89
00:07:54,020 --> 00:07:55,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But His Lordship's going to—</font>

90
00:07:56,080 --> 00:07:58,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What should I do, Scarlett?!</font>

91
00:08:03,340 --> 00:08:04,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This won't be easy.</font>

92
00:08:05,850 --> 00:08:09,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Did Miss Grail make it out safely?</i></font>

93
00:08:14,410 --> 00:08:16,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's funny.</i></font>

94
00:08:16,510 --> 00:08:20,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Amid all this, I only care 
about what happens to her.</i></font>

95
00:08:22,360 --> 00:08:23,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Should I risk it?</font>

96
00:08:32,450 --> 00:08:33,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Scarlett?</font>

97
00:08:36,670 --> 00:08:38,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I asked you to look after Miss Grail...</font>

98
00:08:39,760 --> 00:08:43,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then again, you would never 
take orders from anyone.</font>

99
00:08:43,210 --> 00:08:44,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see him! He's over here!</font>

100
00:08:46,620 --> 00:08:47,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have my thanks.</font>

101
00:08:57,530 --> 00:09:00,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Honestly, you look pathetic.</font>

102
00:09:00,480 --> 00:09:03,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Scarlett! You're not hurt, are you?!</font>

103
00:09:03,740 --> 00:09:07,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course not. Who do you 
think you're talking to?</font>

104
00:09:08,050 --> 00:09:09,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, thank goodness!</font>

105
00:09:14,350 --> 00:09:16,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Lordship!</font>

106
00:09:18,320 --> 00:09:19,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you wounded?</font>

107
00:09:20,120 --> 00:09:22,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought I told you to escape.</font>

108
00:09:22,790 --> 00:09:24,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, Your stupid Lordship!</font>

109
00:09:26,480 --> 00:09:29,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How could I possibly leave you 
in that situation and run away?!</font>

110
00:09:29,990 --> 00:09:31,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, honestly!</font>

111
00:09:32,140 --> 00:09:34,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You... Your Stupidship!</font>

112
00:09:34,380 --> 00:09:35,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Stupidship"?</font>

113
00:09:36,730 --> 00:09:39,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right! You're
 His stupid Lordship! His Stupidship!</font>

114
00:09:39,950 --> 00:09:41,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Does that bother you?!</font>

115
00:09:46,460 --> 00:09:48,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you laughing for?!</font>

116
00:09:50,190 --> 00:09:51,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why...</font>

117
00:09:52,200 --> 00:09:53,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">are you crying?</font>

118
00:09:54,920 --> 00:09:56,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because I was scared!</font>

119
00:09:56,780 --> 00:09:58,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why I told you to escape.</font>

120
00:09:58,100 --> 00:10:01,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No! I was scared because 
I thought you might die!</font>

121
00:10:01,870 --> 00:10:03,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can't you get that through your head?!</font>

122
00:10:03,780 --> 00:10:06,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Stupidship! You big, dumb oaf!</font>

123
00:10:10,770 --> 00:10:11,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I...</font>

124
00:10:12,610 --> 00:10:14,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">was scared too.</font>

125
00:10:15,630 --> 00:10:17,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Scared I might lose you.</font>

126
00:10:22,550 --> 00:10:24,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess we're alike, Connie.</font>

127
00:10:26,930 --> 00:10:31,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-If you think a smile is all it takes to 
placate me, you couldn't be more wrong.</font>

128
00:10:38,900 --> 00:10:40,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If allowed...</font>

129
00:10:44,180 --> 00:10:45,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I'm allowed,</font>

130
00:10:47,690 --> 00:10:51,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I would like to walk 
through life at your side.</font>

131
00:10:54,950 --> 00:10:55,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In that case,</font>

132
00:10:56,880 --> 00:10:58,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll allow it.</font>

133
00:10:59,530 --> 00:11:01,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have my permission.</font>

134
00:11:02,030 --> 00:11:06,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No matter who else withholds theirs, 
and even if the gods object,</font>

135
00:11:07,740 --> 00:11:09,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll allow you everything.</font>

136
00:11:10,060 --> 00:11:14,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So Your Lordship has nothing 
whatsoever to worry about.</font>

137
00:11:17,130 --> 00:11:20,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Should anyone insist on finding fault
 with you in spite of that,</font>

138
00:11:22,290 --> 00:11:23,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll slap them good and proper.</font>

139
00:11:25,480 --> 00:11:27,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What man could resist that line?</font>

140
00:11:29,990 --> 00:11:33,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You say the most outrageous 
things sometimes.</font>

141
00:11:34,060 --> 00:11:36,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I... I know I need to work on that.</font>

142
00:11:41,290 --> 00:11:42,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please do.</font>

143
00:11:50,100 --> 00:11:53,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you're going to blame someone,
blame Abigail.</font>

144
00:11:54,060 --> 00:11:56,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Abby's done nothing wrong.</font>

145
00:11:57,050 --> 00:12:00,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">True. That woman is always in the right.</font>

146
00:12:00,950 --> 00:12:03,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I truly cannot stomach her.</font>

147
00:12:03,570 --> 00:12:09,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Imagine the look on that hypocrite's face 
when I send her your head.</font>

148
00:12:12,140 --> 00:12:14,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, hold it right there.</font>

149
00:12:14,450 --> 00:12:15,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Salvador?</font>

150
00:12:16,490 --> 00:12:18,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll thank you not to interfere.</font>

151
00:12:18,550 --> 00:12:21,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd normally be happy to oblige,</font>

152
00:12:21,480 --> 00:12:24,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I make it my policy not to kill kids.</font>

153
00:12:28,530 --> 00:12:30,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So go back to your convent</font>

154
00:12:32,220 --> 00:12:36,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and keep the Security Force's 
eyes on you.</font>

155
00:12:36,750 --> 00:12:40,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-You dare to treat me like...</font>

156
00:12:40,190 --> 00:12:44,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, but we don't want you
 telling any tales.</font>

157
00:12:44,480 --> 00:12:47,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd prefer to rip out
your tongue, but well...</font>

158
00:12:51,400 --> 00:12:54,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Work her over so she can't talk.</font>

159
00:12:55,450 --> 00:12:59,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No! No!</font>

160
00:13:00,810 --> 00:13:03,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now then, you can run on home.</font>

161
00:13:04,060 --> 00:13:05,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Help...</font>

162
00:13:12,470 --> 00:13:14,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're a sharp one.</font>

163
00:13:20,740 --> 00:13:23,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They were even serving him meals.</font>

164
00:13:24,090 --> 00:13:26,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It certainly looks like
they kept Uly alive.</font>

165
00:13:27,230 --> 00:13:29,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why don't they kill him, though?</font>

166
00:13:31,050 --> 00:13:37,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The fact that Uly was abducted in this 
country is all Faris needs to start a war.</font>

167
00:13:38,250 --> 00:13:44,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Theophilis already acts like he's king. 
His agents would dispose of Uly at once.</font>

168
00:13:45,250 --> 00:13:51,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After all, only he and Uly 
inherited the bluish-violet eyes</font>

169
00:13:51,280 --> 00:13:53,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that mark our royalty.</font>

170
00:13:53,810 --> 00:13:57,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So if Prince Ulysses is being kept alive,</font>

171
00:13:57,520 --> 00:14:00,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Theophilis isn't the one behind this.</font>

172
00:14:01,250 --> 00:14:05,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And the only contender who hasn't 
renounced his right to the throne is...</font>

173
00:14:08,420 --> 00:14:11,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eularia, we're going to see Kendall.</font>

174
00:14:11,770 --> 00:14:13,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our enemy isn't Theophilis.</font>

175
00:14:14,990 --> 00:14:17,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's Second Prince Roderick.</font>

176
00:14:20,790 --> 00:14:23,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where could Lucia have gone?</font>

177
00:14:23,790 --> 00:14:28,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Abigail's people are searching 
and haven't found a clue.</font>

178
00:14:29,810 --> 00:14:33,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And Deborah turned up 
in no condition to talk.</font>

179
00:14:34,290 --> 00:14:36,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What on earth is going on?</font>

180
00:14:36,840 --> 00:14:38,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Constance Grail?</font>

181
00:14:41,910 --> 00:14:43,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's been too long.</font>

182
00:14:44,150 --> 00:14:45,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pamela...</font>

183
00:14:45,890 --> 00:14:49,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You haven't changed a bit.</font>

184
00:14:49,710 --> 00:14:53,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about me? Don't I seem 
a little different to you?</font>

185
00:14:55,420 --> 00:15:00,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To tell the truth,
 I spotted you not long ago.</font>

186
00:15:00,440 --> 00:15:03,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In a warehouse on the Grafton wharf.</font>

187
00:15:03,420 --> 00:15:06,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I th-think you must be mistaken.</font>

188
00:15:06,420 --> 00:15:07,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you now?</font>

189
00:15:09,670 --> 00:15:11,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, it doesn't really matter.</font>

190
00:15:16,950 --> 00:15:19,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">King Ernst is going to Melvina?</font>

191
00:15:20,580 --> 00:15:27,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The grenades at the wharf were made
with smuggled explosives from Melvina.</font>

192
00:15:27,890 --> 00:15:32,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In exchange for overlooking that fact, 
he wants a trade agreement on arms</font>

193
00:15:33,030 --> 00:15:35,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that will act as a check against Faris.</font>

194
00:15:36,490 --> 00:15:38,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Explosives from Melvina...?</font>

195
00:15:39,240 --> 00:15:41,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lily mentioned that in her letter.</font>

196
00:15:43,020 --> 00:15:46,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm having explosives 
smuggled in from Melvina.</font>

197
00:15:47,090 --> 00:15:49,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Crown Princess Cecilia!</font>

198
00:15:52,570 --> 00:15:54,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's the meaning of this?!</font>

199
00:15:54,910 --> 00:15:59,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You never breathed a word 
of a pact with Melvina to me!</font>

200
00:15:59,310 --> 00:16:01,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A strange reaction.</font>

201
00:16:01,240 --> 00:16:04,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Melvina borders the Luze domain 
where you grew up.</font>

202
00:16:04,530 --> 00:16:08,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And all the agreement will do is 
let us trade freely with them.</font>

203
00:16:09,120 --> 00:16:11,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, why are you so flustered?</font>

204
00:16:13,410 --> 00:16:16,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've waited a long time for this day,</font>

205
00:16:16,980 --> 00:16:21,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">when the explosives you smuggled in 
saw use on our soil.</font>

206
00:16:23,540 --> 00:16:25,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How long have you known?</font>

207
00:16:26,080 --> 00:16:30,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why do you think I married you 
despite objections from all sides?</font>

208
00:16:30,960 --> 00:16:35,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why do you think my father 
and Duke Castiel gave their blessings?</font>

209
00:16:35,990 --> 00:16:37,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">From the very beginning?</font>

210
00:16:39,970 --> 00:16:45,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this wise? You could be 
accused yourself if word gets out.</font>

211
00:16:46,920 --> 00:16:48,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Didn't you know?</font>

212
00:16:52,290 --> 00:16:56,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been guilty for a long time now.</font>

213
00:17:01,380 --> 00:17:04,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I always knew you were careless.</font>

214
00:17:09,590 --> 00:17:13,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come quickly! Enrique's having a fit!</font>

215
00:17:17,470 --> 00:17:19,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You didn't kill him?</font>

216
00:17:19,860 --> 00:17:24,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He is still a prince. It's easier 
for me to act with him alive.</font>

217
00:17:25,870 --> 00:17:27,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

218
00:17:27,790 --> 00:17:30,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They've already moved Ulysses 
to that dungeon.</font>

219
00:17:31,100 --> 00:17:33,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now everything is in place.</font>

220
00:17:34,330 --> 00:17:37,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, there have been many 
unforeseen developments,</font>

221
00:17:38,080 --> 00:17:40,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but now is our time to strike.</font>

222
00:17:41,350 --> 00:17:43,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, but first...</font>

223
00:17:46,840 --> 00:17:50,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we must dispose of nuisances.</font>

224
00:17:56,040 --> 00:17:58,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really, it was only by chance!</font>

225
00:17:59,230 --> 00:18:01,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Extra! Extra!</font>

226
00:18:01,810 --> 00:18:03,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A prince was kidnapped?!</font>

227
00:18:03,800 --> 00:18:06,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They say Faris is ready to go to war!</font>

228
00:18:07,610 --> 00:18:12,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I went to the Grafton domain 
on my physician's advice.</font>

229
00:18:12,790 --> 00:18:14,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And there, I just so happened</font>

230
00:18:14,680 --> 00:18:19,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to witness a friend of mine 
shove a sobbing child into a carriage.</font>

231
00:18:19,330 --> 00:18:22,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I couldn't put it out of my mind,</font>

232
00:18:22,060 --> 00:18:24,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I asked her about it.</font>

233
00:18:24,580 --> 00:18:28,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But she panicked and told me
 I had to be mistaken.</font>

234
00:18:29,430 --> 00:18:30,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looking back, I realize...</font>

235
00:18:30,590 --> 00:18:33,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that must have been Prince Ulysses.</font>

236
00:18:35,030 --> 00:18:36,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, that's their game.</font>

237
00:18:36,750 --> 00:18:39,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Constance Grail, I believe?</font>

238
00:18:39,600 --> 00:18:44,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hereby arrest you for aiding and 
abetting the abduction of Ulysses Faris.</font>

239
00:18:47,230 --> 00:18:49,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've done nothing wrong.</font>

240
00:18:49,740 --> 00:18:52,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did Randolph Ulster do the dirty work?</font>

241
00:18:54,950 --> 00:18:59,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We have testimony
 that Ulster drew his gun.</font>

242
00:19:00,400 --> 00:19:02,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So that's how it's going to be.</i></font>

243
00:19:02,730 --> 00:19:06,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Someone must be questioning 
His Lordship as we speak.</i></font>

244
00:19:06,400 --> 00:19:12,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Time wasted on us delays the search for 
Prince Ulysses and moves us closer to war.</i></font>

245
00:19:15,320 --> 00:19:16,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Connie?</font>

246
00:19:16,640 --> 00:19:21,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No. I was a party to the abduction 
of Prince Ulysses.</font>

247
00:19:23,180 --> 00:19:24,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I had backers.</font>

248
00:19:25,450 --> 00:19:30,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ruthless criminals who don't hesitate 
to kill to get what they want.</font>

249
00:19:30,010 --> 00:19:31,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You wouldn't!</font>

250
00:19:31,880 --> 00:19:33,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The name of their organization...</font>

251
00:19:33,270 --> 00:19:34,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, wait!</font>

252
00:19:35,370 --> 00:19:36,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is Daeg Gallus.</font>

253
00:19:38,290 --> 00:19:40,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Connie, you idiot!</font>

254
00:19:40,380 --> 00:19:42,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you get all that?</font>

255
00:19:43,410 --> 00:19:45,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have more to confess.</font>

256
00:19:45,470 --> 00:19:47,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop. That's enough.</font>

257
00:19:48,150 --> 00:19:49,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In that case,</font>

258
00:19:50,550 --> 00:19:52,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">please summon Viscount Hamsworth.</font>

259
00:19:53,840 --> 00:19:56,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My engagement to Earl Randolph Ulster...</font>

260
00:19:58,050 --> 00:19:59,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">must be broken off.</font>

261
00:20:03,300 --> 00:20:05,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Lordship! So they let you go.</font>

262
00:20:07,090 --> 00:20:09,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you thinking?!</font>

263
00:20:09,180 --> 00:20:14,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You won't be free to act 
unless we sever all ties.</font>

264
00:20:16,430 --> 00:20:19,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're going to cast me off?</font>

265
00:20:24,540 --> 00:20:29,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If the day comes when this is all over 
and we can laugh together again,</font>

266
00:20:29,950 --> 00:20:32,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd like to drop in on 
a certain someone uninvited.</font>

267
00:20:34,200 --> 00:20:40,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That someone is strong and kind 
and always in the right,</font>

268
00:20:40,570 --> 00:20:46,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but he's such an oaf that he's convinced 
himself he can't make anyone happy.</font>

269
00:20:48,240 --> 00:20:52,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, this time, I want to be 
the one to take him by the hand.</font>

270
00:20:54,890 --> 00:20:56,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That will prove difficult.</font>

271
00:20:58,980 --> 00:21:01,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm certain you'll be proposed to first...</font>

272
00:21:03,120 --> 00:21:09,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">by a dull man who can't manage a witty 
remark or pick a decent spot for a date.</font>

273
00:21:26,680 --> 00:21:28,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">On my forehead?</font>

274
00:21:28,930 --> 00:21:31,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not engaged to you at the moment.</font>

275
00:21:37,080 --> 00:21:38,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Royal Highness Prince Johan,</font>

276
00:21:40,230 --> 00:21:42,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">have you reached a decision?</font>

277
00:21:43,140 --> 00:21:47,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How many times must I tell you?
 I'm only standing in for the king.</font>

278
00:21:44,190 --> 00:21:47,650
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}SECOND PRINCE JOHAN ADELBIDE</font>

279
00:21:51,220 --> 00:21:53,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Villain! This is my daughter's!</font>

280
00:21:53,400 --> 00:21:58,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have no fear. Your precious daughter 
has not suffered a scratch...</font>

281
00:21:59,050 --> 00:22:01,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">for the moment.</font>

282
00:22:02,960 --> 00:22:06,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Faris desires war.</font>

283
00:22:06,130 --> 00:22:08,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To convince them to
 stay their raised fist,</font>

284
00:22:08,800 --> 00:22:11,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you must make an example</font>

285
00:22:12,050 --> 00:22:14,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">by publicly executing...</font>

286
00:22:14,730 --> 00:22:18,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the kidnapper, Constance Grail.</font>

287
00:22:19,980 --> 00:22:22,060
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}FOR THE FUTURE</font>

288
00:22:29,680 --> 00:22:33,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font size="10"><font face="Arial"><font color="#511f35">Translation:
<font size="12">William Varteresian</font></font></font></font></font>

